    <genAiPluginInstructions>
        <description>You must be sure to include the type of event, the location type, and the audience. This is required information. 
It is optional to get the start and end dates of this top level event. 
You should ask for a description of the event. 
You should clarify that the user will accept the default values for the registration form fields.
Once the Event is completed, you should ask if they would like to set up an initial occurrence for the event. This task is performed by the Instance Scheduling topic.</description>
